 Scheme
==============================

 CLI YAML
  |   |
  |   |
  |   |           Output
  |   |
  |   |	           ^  ^ 
  |   |            |  |
  V   V   +--------+  |
          |           |
Configuration -->  Run  <-- StepDefinitions
  |
  |                ^  ^
  |                |  |
  |     +----------+  +-----------+
  |	    |      	                  |
  | Reporter                  Scenarios <-- Grammar <-- Languages
  |                                                        
  |                                                        ^
  |                                                        |
  +--------------------------------------------------------+


 Options
==============================
 require, guess => StepDefinitions
 (args), exclude => Features, StepDefinitions
 language => Features
 out, [no-]color, no-multiline, no-source, no-snippets, backtrace => Reporter
 format, profile, dry-run, autoformat => (main)
 tags, scenario_names => Run
 strict  => Context
 verbose => Reporter, (...)
 quiet => (alias for set of options)


